Exclusion criteria: Total persons in the data instance
Sex or birth year missing or absurd or no dates of entry or exit, or incomplete date of death or birth, or observation period too short
Exit from data source before 1 Jan 2017
No disease codes identified after study entry
Other criteria suggesting the disease is present during lookback
Persons dying before entrance in the follow-up
Persons leaving alive the cohort before entering the follow-up (censoring)
